This update fixes an issue with the display of games in iOS 8 on iPad.

This update fixes an issue some Fit Brains members were seeing when playing the new Language games. 

Happy Brain Training!

Rosetta Stone Fit Brains is proud to launch 2 new games for the Language brain area! 

Happy Brain Training!

New updates (below), bug fixes, app optimization

BETTER THAN EVER: The new Fit Brains logo & design is all about connectivity.  Our brain has a wide range of cognitive skills. We can train each skill individually, but these brain areas need to operate together efficiently for your brain to perform at peak levels. Fit Brains offers innovative training for every crucial area of your brain and creates fluid connections between improved brain skills. Fit Brains is directly connected to your health & education, include Fit Brains training in your daily regime to ensure lifelong learning, mind health, and body health.
Bug fixes and optimizations

- Adds integration with our upcoming Fit Brains Language Trainer.
- Fixes a bug that could cause the trainer to crash while playing Coin Calc.
- Fixes a bug which caused Find It Fast to mark some correct answers as incorrect.
- Additional bug fixes and optimizations.
This update adds integration with our upcoming Fit Brains Logic Trainer

- New brain area sub-measures: see more detailed information about each of the 5 areas of the brain from the Performance Tab.
- Bug fixes and optimization improvements.
- Additional optimizations for older devices (iOS5).

NEW FEATURE - Fit Brains Network sync! Create a password and sync your app(s) with the Fit Brains Network for improved stats sharing between devices and other Fit Brains apps.

NEW DESIGN - Brand new app design to compliment the look and feel of iOS7!

UPDATED SCORING - Each brain game contributes up to 100 points to your total Fit Brains Index. As we launch new games, your maximum potential points will increase.

Additional bug fixes and app optimizations

description.standard:
Rosetta Stone Fit Brains Trainer is an award-winning brain training & fitness app brought to you by Rosetta Stone, the world's premier learning company. Fit Brains games are not only extremely fun to play, but they help improve your brain health as well. Train your brain with over 360 brain games & workout sessions designed to target Memory, Processing Speed, Concentration, Problem Solving, and Visual-Spatial skills. Download the Fit Brains app for FREE now! 

HEALTH BENEFITS:  

* Improve Memory and Recognition 
* Deep Concentration 
* Increase Attention Span
* Higher Mental IQ
* Smart & Quick Thinking 
* Stronger Problem Solving
* Improve Hand-Eye Coordination
* Faster Reaction Speed
* Positive Mood Changes  

AWARD-WINNING BRAIN TRAINING BY ROSETTA STONE: The Fit Brains Trainer app has been downloaded by over 10 million people, ranked #1 education app in 90+ countries, and is a regularly featured app with more than 100,000 ratings averaging 4.5 stars worldwide! The Fit Brains Trainer app is a part of Rosetta Stone's award-winning Fit Brains Brain Training Program, which includes a full web training program + 7 targeted brain apps. Visit www.fitbrains.com for more info! 

TRACK YOUR PERFORMANCE: 
The Fit Brains Index uses an innovative adaptive learning system to scale and measures your cognitive performances across 5 major brain areas. Use personalized tools to track & improve your performance, and compare your training scores with others your age and gender. 

HOW TO SYNC YOUR FIT BRAINS ACCOUNT: Use the same Fit Brains Network account for all your Fit Brains apps on all your devices. Check your account by going to the "Training" tab & pull down the "Connect to Fit Brains" bar. Green = Signed in. Orange = Tap the bar and create a Fit Brains Network profile. When you open an app for the 1st time, choose "Existing User" and sign in with your Fit Brains Network account. If you’ve already opened the app, press "Settings" tab, press "Switch Users", "Sign into Fit Brains", and sign in with your universal Fit Brains Network account. 

Try our other fun brain fitness & health products: 

- The Fit Brains Complete Program: Join our full program to access unlimited web brain training & 7 unlocked Fit Brains iOS apps (www.fitbrains.com )
- Fit Brains for Kids: Sparky's Adventures 
- Fit Brains Focus Trainer 
- Fit Brains Memory Trainer 
- Fit Brains Speed Trainer 
- Fit Brains Visual Trainer 
- Fit Brains Logic Trainer 
- Fit Brains Language Trainer 
- Fit Brains: Brain Health Lifestyle® Assessment 
- Fit Brains: Cognitive Assessment 

CONTACT US 

GENERAL INQUIRIES: contact@fitbrains.com
WEBSITE: http://www.fitbrains.com  
TWITTER: http://twitter.com/fitbrains 
 FACEBOOK: http://www.facebook.com/FitBrainsCommunity 
BLOG: http://www.fitbrains.com /blog 
LINKEDIN: http://www.linkedin.com/company/fit-brains 
PINTEREST: http://www.pinterest.com/rosettastonehq/fit-brains-brain-games/

SCIENCE OF FIT BRAINS 

Our scientific efforts are led by our Chief Scientific Officer, Dr. Paul Nussbaum, a clinical neuropsychologist and national leader in Brain Health. He is cited frequently by the media and national press including the New York Times, Wall Street Journal and USA Today.


IN THE NEWS 

New York Times:  
"There is a gradual growing awareness that challenging your brain can have positive effects," Dr. Cohen said... "Every time you challenge your brain it will actually modify the brain," he said. "We can indeed form new brain cells, despite a century of being told it is impossible."

 "I logged on during a break at work and got so hooked I ended up playing their brain games for an hour." 

Discover Magazine: 
 "What's unique: Complex, richly illustrated and thought out brain games with different levels and storylines. Summed up: Very dynamic." 

  CBS: 
 "It's a game playing product but the twist here is that all of the games help exercise and train your brain!"
